Title: Celebrating the Bicentennial of the birth of Herman Melville, American novelist, short story writer, and poet of the American Renaissance period
ActClause: LEGISLATIVE RESOLUTION celebrating the Bicentennial of the birth of Herman Melville, American novelist, short story writer, and poet of the American Renaissance period who was a long-time resident of New York State, including Lansingburgh, Albany and New York City to be celebrated on August 3, 2019
